('95695','33008','5','Villa Beach House Style in Porto Andratx for sale'),
('95696','33009','5','Porto Andratx is one of the most popular residential areas in the southwest of Mallorca. This villa stands on a 1,300m² large hillside plot with fantastic views over the harbor entrance and the mountains of Puerto Andratx. It was renovated in recent years and equipped with high-quality materials, such as limed Oak parquet floors, underfloor heating (oil / water), air-conditioning h / c, fireplace, modern open kitchen with cooking island, wooden double-glazed windows, BUS home automation etc. The 387m² living space is spread over 2 levels. On the ground floor are the entrance hall, kitchen, utility room, dining room, living room, office room, guest room with bathroom and guest toilet. On the 1st floor has a master bedroom with bathroom en suite, dressing room, terrace and 3 bedrooms and a bathroom.\r\nThree garages, covered- and open terraces, barbecue area, a sauna room with shower and toilet as well as a swimming pool with sun terraces complete the offer\r\n'),
